OL,3,CMurder investigation underway
OL,4,Cfollowing discovery of body in
OL,5,CLeicester
OL,7,FA murder investigation has been
OL,8,Flaunched following the discovery of a
OL,9,Fbody in Castle Gardens, in Leicester,
OL,10,Fon Thursday evening.
OL,12,FLeicestershire Police received a call
OL,13,Fat 7.58pm reporting a dead body in a
OL,14,Fbush.
OL,16,FOfficers attended, along with East
OL,17,FMidlands Ambulance Service, and a man
OL,18,F` who was in his 40s ` was pronounced
OL,19,Fdead at the scene.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
