OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1778249473
OL,3,CMurder investigation underway
OL,4,Cfollowing discovery of body in
OL,5,CLeicester
OL,7,FDetectives say they are working to
OL,8,Festablish the circumstances
OL,9,Fsurrounding the man's death and there
OL,10,Fis a significant police presence in
OL,11,Fthe area.
OL,13,FThere is also a scene on at an address
OL,14,Fin Beacon Close in Beaumont Leys. This
OL,15,Fis connected to this investigation.
OL,17,FTwo people are in custody on suspicion
OL,18,Fof murder. A 46-year-old woman and a
OL,19,F76-year-old man, both from Leicester,
OL,20,Fare being questioned by detectives.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
