PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1778249473
OL,3,CMurder investigation underway
OL,4,Cfollowing discovery of body in
OL,5,CLeicester
OL,7,FDetective Inspector Lorna Granville
OL,8,Ffrom the East Midlands Special
OL,9,FOperations Unit is leading the
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,FShe said: "Work is being carried out
OL,13,Fto determine what has happened to lead
OL,14,Fto this man's death. To allow this to
OL,15,Fhappen, there is a cordon in place in
OL,16,FCastle Gardens, preventing access.
OL,18,F"Trawls of CCTV in the area are being
OL,19,Fcarried out and witnesses are being
OL,20,Fspoken to.
OL,26,@tD@KOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
