PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1778249473
OL,3,CMurder investigation underway
OL,4,Cfollowing discovery of body in
OL,5,CLeicester
OL,7,F"Anyone in the area of Castle Gardens
OL,8,Fat around 8pm last night (Thursday) is
OL,9,Fasked to contact police with any
OL,10,Finformation. Did you see anyone acting
OL,11,Fin a suspicious way?
OL,13,F"Any information may prove helpful to
OL,14,Fthe investigation, no matter how
OL,15,Finsignificant it may seem to you.
OL,17,F"There is also a cordon in place at an
OL,18,Faddress in Beacon Close, Beaumont
OL,19,FLeys, in connection with this
OL,20,Finvestigation and searches are being
OL,21,Fcarried out there.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
